		"description": "<p><em><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e3cae755-7fff-059f-8401-07f0594a9c74\"><strong>Type:</strong> Substance; <strong>Level:</strong> 5; <strong>Element:</strong> Lightning</span></em></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-52c65750-7fff-d084-b270-0865634182af\">By spending 3 spell points, your blast clings to targets who are hit or who fail their save, dealing 1d6 ongoing damage of the same type for 1 minute. Targets may attempt a saving throw (Dex for Fire, Con for Cold or Lightning) to end the effect at the end of their turn, or they can end it automatically as an action. For every 2 additional spell points you spend, increase the ongoing damage by +1d6.</span></p>",
